    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver despite some visible signs of age. The exterior shows several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, while the interior has some moderate wear on the upholstery and minor staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it may soon require routine maintenance for wear-and-tear items like brakes or tires. It is a solid, functional choice for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
