    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine runs but suffers from frequent stalling and fluid leaks, while the transmission shifts roughly. The exterior shows heavy wear including noticeable rust patches, fading paint, and several dents, and the interior has sustained significant wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is recommended as a project car or for parts, and a professional inspection is highly advised before any attempt at regular use.",
