      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and well-maintained ride? This vehicle is in good condition and ready for its next owner! It features a clean interior, a smooth engine, and has been consistently serviced to ensure a dependable driving experience. It's a fantastic value for anyone seeking a quality car that looks great and performs even better on the road!",
