    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality masterpiece characterized by its flawless aesthetic and mechanical integrity. Every detail, from the pristine upholstery to the lustrous exterior finish, reflects a history of meticulous care. We invite discerning buyers to experience a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market, offering unrivaled refinement and investment-grade quality.",
      "price": 43500.0,
